{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Proper noun===
'''[[New]] [[York]] [[City]]'''

# [[New York, New York]], the largest city in the [[United States of America]]. It consists of five [[borough]]s: [[Manhattan]], the [[Bronx]], [[Brooklyn]], [[Queens]] and [[Staten Island]]. Situated at the mouth of the [[Hudson River]] in [[New York State]].
# [[Manhattan]].

====Usage notes====
The term ''New York City'' can refer to the island of Manhattan alone but most often refers to the entire city. The city’s official name is simply [[New York]], but is referred to as [[New York City]] or [[New York, New York]] to distinguish it from [[New York State]].

